reviewText: Good comedy. John barrymore isn't that funny, though. The rest of the cast is top notch.
Great movie. Purchased for my husband. He was very pleased with it.

As you watch this film you feel like you are watching present day politicians doing things proper and things improper so long as they can be re-elected. Here is a chance to see the great John Barrymore in a terrific comedy giving a great performance. If you want a good evenings entertainment with lots of laughs and a keen insight into the political mind, this is the film for you!
